eNCA's Moloko Moloto reprots. Courtesy #DStv403 BLOEMFONTEIN - The Provincial Executive Committee of the ANC in the Free State has decided to recall current Premier Sisi Ntombela after losing the chairperson position to Mxolisi Dukwana. Reports suggest that Ntombela and eight MECs face the axe. This is the new provincial leadership's effort to stem internal squabbles and get service delivery back on track.